--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Neural Network

    Current version:     0.1.0
    Author:              Rikard Johansson

    Simple neural network written in c. Developed in a dynamic way for easy
    learning of different data types.

    This project was originally deveoped during a university project where the
    purpose was to identify a coffecup in an image taken by a camera mounted on
    a moving robot. We ran the image through some filters to get the contours
    which we converted to a polygon and passed to the neural network. I wanted
    to train the network on my computer to make loading time more efficient on
    the embedded device, which is the reason for simple dump and load from a
    textfile.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


